---
title: Sesame Sweet Soy Fried Rice with Carrots, Snap Peas, a Fried Egg & Sriracha Mayo
description: Is there anything better than curling up with a bowl of fried rice? Our answer: not really! This week, our chefs cooked up a vegetarian version of the classic comfort food that’s got it all: tender carrots and snap peas, a tantalizing sesame soy sauce, fried eggs, and pan-crisped rice. The result? A symphony of flavors and textures you’ll find yourself craving again and again.
